      "text": "I love Advent of Code and especially exactly this kind of community approach of learning from each other, sharing solutions and becoming better developers while having a lot of fun.\n\nPretty much every dev community I'm in is buzzing in their Advent of Code channel, happy to see same is happening at junior.guru community as well!",
